{
  "stem": "5496.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was mostly German women who came out there, and they were doing the count.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they came with their beautiful, freshly-ironed blouses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they wore boots.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And to this day, I hate culottes, they all wore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I-- and you know, what you do for horses and all that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The whip, in her hand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Grandmother was gone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't have her with.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we just-- I don't remember, except that we-- she must have felt terrible, for to see her children.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we felt, in turn, terrible for her being out there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And each day's selection came while we were on the zahlappell.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Each day was a selection, and each day we were grateful that we are still together.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that went on until the day that will live in infamy, October 10, 1944, when Mengele came to the barracks, himself.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was the final selection.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And while my aunt and I went to the right, my sister and mother to the left.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's the last time that I have seen them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were taken from there to a railroad station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't know where we go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was dark.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they told us again, we're going to some showers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So obviously, we must have gone through some kind of a disinfecting station.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the next thing I knew, I was again on a train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they took us to a place that I cannot find on the map.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were the so-called able-bodied, my aunt and I.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there was a relatively small camp, women only.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we were taken for slave labor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were digging ditches, anti-tank ditches.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they took us out every morning in this bitter cold, with a little rag on our bones.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
